  <section id="security-sect-install-ldap">
    <title>Installing LDAP Plugin</title>

    <para>To install the Procurement Suite, grab the
    <filename>nexus-plugin-realm-ldap-1.0-SNAPSHOT-plugin.zip</filename> and
    unpack this archive in your
    <filename>\${NEXUS_HOME}/runtime/apps/nexus/lib</filename> directory. This
    will install the Nexus LDAP Plugin and all the required JARs in your Nexus
    classpath.</para>
  </section>

